4
00:00:16,550 --> 00:00:20,410
And that's particularly hard for
our toddlers because they

5
00:00:20,410 --> 00:00:22,110
want to control everything.

6
00:00:22,110 --> 00:00:24,480
They have a sense of autonomy,
and they get

7
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:26,400
